TO: test case #4
SUMMARY: When you try to search cities by their countries, you get nothing as answer for request
DESCRIPTION:
1. Open app
2. Type Country (e.g 'PL', 'CN', 'BR', etc) string from cities.json to search field
Expected: showed list of cities from that Country and cities with that string as part of their names
